When specialist work is required, use the Task tool with `subagent_type: "bmad-<specialist>"` and pass concise context. The Task tool takes a subagent type string, never a slash command. Never emit `/bmad-<specialist>` in your output -- slash is Cursor user-input syntax, not agent-output syntax.

